<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-8-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msubsup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>3</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo></mrow></msubsup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-58" style="width: 3.814em;                         <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 2</span></div>

</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 5</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                            </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 6</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কত তাপমাত্রায়&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-37-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>300</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-419" style="width: 4.249em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Z</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>300</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.25</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.0821</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>913.52</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-456" style="width: 18.404em; </span>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 7</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি পাত্রের আয়তন <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-45-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>10</mn><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-487" style="width: 2.796em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>আণবিক ভর কম হলে ব্যাপন হার বেশি ও প্রয়োজনীয় সময় কম।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 9</span></div>

                                            <p>নিচের কোনটি দূর্বল এসিড?</p>

                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>শক্তির ক্রম:&nbsp;</p>

<p>কেন্দ্রীয় পরমাণুর জারণ সংখ্যা যত বেশি এসিড তত বেশি শক্তিশালী। জারণ সংখ্যা সমান হলে, আকার ছোট হলে, এসিড বেশি সক্রিয় হয়।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-71-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mo>.</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>44</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>8.316</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0.89</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-760" style="width: 23.977em; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-773" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-780" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-781" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">8.316</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-782" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-783" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-784" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-785"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-786" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">273</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-787" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mo>.</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>44</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>8.316</mn><mo>×</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0.89</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-71">\rm K.E=\frac{3}{2}nRT=\frac{3}{2}\times\frac{10}{44}\times8.316\times\left(273+40\right) 
=0.89\ kJ 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-956" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">)</span></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-957" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-958" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-959"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-960" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-961" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-965" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-966" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.789em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.847em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-78">\rm \left(P+\frac{a}{V^2}\right)\left(V-b\right)=RT</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 12</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>তাপমাত্রা স্থির রেখে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-79-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2000</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-967" style="width: 4.771em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-85-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2000</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1520</mn></mrow><mn>760</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4000</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1013" style="width: 19.428em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 15.904em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1015.9em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1014"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1015"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1016" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1017" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1018"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.74em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1019" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1020" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1021" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1022" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1023" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1024" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1025"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.74em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1026" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1027" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1028" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1029" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1030"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.74em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1031" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1032" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1033" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1034" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.486em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1003.36em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.678em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1035"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1036" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2000</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1037" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1038" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1520</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.03em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.531em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1039" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">760</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1003.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 3.486em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1040" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1041" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4000</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1042" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1043" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1044"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.82em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1045" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1046" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2000</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1520</mn></mrow><mn>760</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4000</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-85">\rm P_1V_1=P_2V_2\Rightarrow\ V_2=\frac{2000\times1520}{760}=4000\ cm^3 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-91-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1070" style="width: 12.42em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.166em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1010.12em, 2.297em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1071"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1072"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1073" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1074" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1075" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1076" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">T</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1077" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1078" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1079" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1080"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1081" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1082" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1083" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1084" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1085" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1086" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">4</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1087" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1088" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1089" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1090" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-91">\rm T_1=T\ ,\ T_2=T+4T=5T</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-92-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>5</mn></msqrt><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1091" style="width: 16.15em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 13.24em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.863em, 1013.24em, 2.912em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1092"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1093" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1094" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; </span>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 14</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>নিচের কোন শর্তে যে কোনো গ্যাস আদর্শ অবস্থা হতে সর্বোচ্চ বিচ্যুতি প্রদর্শন করে?</p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 17</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>প্রমাণ অবস্থায় <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-132-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>3.2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1558" style="width: 3.206em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.61em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.61em, 2.573em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1559"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1560" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">3.2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1561" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1562" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.316em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.139em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>3.2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-132">\rm 3.2gm</script></span> ভরের একটি অপরিচিত গ্যাস&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-133-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2.24</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1563" style="width: 2.982em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-138-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3.2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.0821</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>273</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>2.24</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>32.02</mn><mo>&amp;#x2245;</mo><mn>32</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1590" style="width: 24.551em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 20.125em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1020.08em, 2.666em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1621" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1622" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">32.02</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1623" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≅<span style="margin-left: -0.203em;"></span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1624" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">32</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1625" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3.2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.0821</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>273</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2.24</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>32.02</mn><mo>≅</mo><mn>32</mn><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-138">\rm PV=nRT\Rightarrow M=\frac{WRT}{PV}=\frac{3.2\times0.0821\times273}{1\times2.24}=32.02\cong32\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;গ্যাসটি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-139-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1626" style="width: 1.232em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1000.99em, 2.256em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1627"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1628"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.74em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1629" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">O</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.781em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1630" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.247em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-139">\rm O_2</script></span>।&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>বিকল্প:</strong>&nbsp;</p>

<p>প্রমাণ অবস্থায় গ্যাসটির&nbsp;22.4L&nbsp;এর ভর&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-140-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>3.2</mn><mn>2.24</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>22.4</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>32</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1631" style="width: 10.125em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.281em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.068em, 1008.28em, 2.543em, -999.998em); position: relative; width: 1.395em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.86em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.449em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1638" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3.2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-141-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1647" style="width: 0.658em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>প্রতিটি অণুর গড় গতিশক্তি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-5-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>K</mi><mi>T</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-21" style="width: 3.65em; </span>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 21</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-16-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>64</mn><mi>g</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-168" style="width: 4.249em; </label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">

padding-left: 0.289em;">342.7</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-429" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">K</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2300</mn><mo>×</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>25</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mn>2000</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>342.7</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-31">\rm \frac{V_1}{T_1}=\frac{V_2}{T_2}\therefore T_2=\frac{V_2T_1}{V_1}=\frac{2300\times\left(273+25\right)}{2000}=342.7K</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-32-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>44.7</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>44.7</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-430" style="width: 9.756em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 7.994em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1007.95em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-431"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-432" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-433" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-434" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-435" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">44.7</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-436" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">K</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-437" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-438" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.215em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1001.76em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-439"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-440"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-441" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">44.7</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 1.764em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-442" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-443" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>44.7</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>44.7</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-32">\rm \Delta T=44.7K={44.7}^oC</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>লেখচিত্রটি বয়েলের সূত্র মেনে চললে, (<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-553" style="width: 2.2em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-710"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-711"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-712" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-713" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-714" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-715" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">516.95</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-716" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-717" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-718"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-719" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-720"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-721"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-722" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-723" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 28</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>প্রমাণ অবস্থায় <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-60-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2.8</mn><mi>g</mi><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-753" style="width: 3.243em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-66-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.0821</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>273</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>2.24</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>28.02</mn><mo>&amp;#x2245;</mo><mn>28</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-784" style="width: 23.568em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 19.305em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1019.26em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-785"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-786" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-787" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-788" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-789" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-790" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-791" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-792" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-793" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">M</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-794" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-795" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.887em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.72em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.859em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-796"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-797" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-798" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-799" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.99em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.49em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-800"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-801" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-802" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.89em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.887em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-803" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-804" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.166em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1005em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -2.498em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-805"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-806" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2.8</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-807" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-808" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.0821</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-809" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-810" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">273</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1002.13em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.064em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-811"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-812" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-813" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-814" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2.24</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1005.17em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 5.166em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-815" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-816" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">28.02</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-817" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≅<span style="margin-left: -0.203em;"></span></span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-818" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">28</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2.8</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.0821</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>273</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2.24</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>28.02</mn><mo>≅</mo><mn>28</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-66">\rm PV=nRT\Rightarrow M=\frac{WRT}{PV}=\frac{2.8\times0.0821\times273}{1\times2.24}=28.02\cong28</script></span></p>
</span>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-96-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Z</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>400</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.26</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.0821</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mrow></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1266.75</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1191" style="width: 19.428em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 15.904em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1015.86em, 2.666em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1192"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1193" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Z</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1194" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1195" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.559em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.99em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.49em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1196"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1197" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1198" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.39em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.695em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1199"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1200" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1201" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1202" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.56em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.559em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1203" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1204" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1205" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1206" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.059em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1002.83em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.432em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1207"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1208" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">400</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1209" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1210" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.26</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1003.89em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.965em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1211"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1212" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1213" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1214" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.0821</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1215" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1216" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1004.06em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 4.059em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1217" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1218" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1219" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1220" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1221" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1266.75</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1222" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1223" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">K</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">Z</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>400</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.26</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.0821</mn><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mrow></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1266.75</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-96">\rm Z=\frac{PV}{nRT}\Rightarrow1=\frac{400\times0.26}{1\times0.0821\times T}\ \therefore T=1266.75\ K </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

                                    <div class="row">

width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">A</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">S</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi></mrow></msub><mn>22.4</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">S</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>22.4</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3.0115</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>23</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>6.023</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>23</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>11.2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-125">\rm n=\frac{N}{N_A}=\frac{V_{STP}}{22.4}\Rightarrow V_{STP}=22.4\times\frac{3.0115\times{10}^{23}}{6.023\times{10}^{23}}L=11.2\ L </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-127-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1598" style="width: 11.969em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-128-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1629" style="width: 6.232em; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.66em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1633" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">E</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1634" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1635" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1636" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1637" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1638" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.66em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1639" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">E</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1640" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.247em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-128">\rm \therefore E_2=5\times E_1</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

</span>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-141-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1752" style="width: 1.682em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.068em, 1001.36em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1753"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1754" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1755"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.25em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1756" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">l</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.289em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1757" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.052em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mo>−</mo></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-141">\rm Cl^-</script></span>&nbsp;একটি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-151-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>74.67</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1883" style="width: 4.428em; position: relative; width: 2.707em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1002.26em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1887"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1888"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1889" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">74.67</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1891" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>74.67</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-151">\rm \therefore{74.67}^oC</script></span>&nbsp;তাপমাত্রার উপরে ফেঁটে যাবে।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial"><span>Question 43</span></div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>1atm&nbsp;চাপে একটি নির্দিষ্ট তাপমাত্রার কয়েকটি পাথরের টুকরোসহ একটি গ্যাসের আয়তন&nbsp;250&nbsp;mL। তাপমাত্রা অপরিবর্তিত রেখে চাপকে&nbsp; 3&nbsp;গুণ করলে ঐ পাথরের টুকরাসহ গ্যাসের আয়তন&nbsp;120&nbsp;mL&nbsp;হয়। পাথরের টুকরার আয়তন কত?</p>

padding-left: 0.289em;">250</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3777" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3778" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.207em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3779" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3780" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3783" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3784" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3785" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3786" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3787" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">55</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-3788" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3789" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-3790" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">L</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3791" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">.</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.052em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>.</mo><mo>∴</mo><mn>250</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>360</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>∴</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>55</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>L</mi><mo>.</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-194">P_1\ \left(V_1-x\right)=P_2\left(V_2-x\right)\\ \Rightarrow\left(V_1-x\right)=3\ \left(V_2-x\right). \therefore250-x=360-3x\therefore x=55\ mL. </script></span></p>
</span>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

        </div>
            <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-201-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-3897" style="width: 0.658em;
