display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.977em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1003.94em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3901"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3902"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3903" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-3904"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3905" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3906" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3907" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">1</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3908" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-3909" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3910" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>4</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-202">\left(4-1\right)=3 </script></span>&nbsp;গুণ বৃদ্ধি পাবে।&nbsp;</p>
</span>
            </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row question">
        <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial"><span>Question 48</span></div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>কোন যৌগটির অম্লধর্মীতা আরহেনিয়াস তত্ত্ব দ্বারা ব্যাখ্যা করা সম্ভব?</p>

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">

            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial"><span>Question 49</span></div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>1L,&nbsp;3L,&nbsp;4L&nbsp;আয়তনের তিনটি পাত্র একটি নির্দিষ্ট তাপমাত্রায় যথাক্রমে&nbsp;4,&nbsp;4&nbsp;এবং&nbsp;6atm&nbsp;চাপে গ্যাস দ্বারা পূর্ণ। পাত্র 3&nbsp;টি পরস্পর সংযুক্ত করলে গ্যাসের মোট চাপ কত &nbsp;হবে?</p>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4114" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4115" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4116" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4117" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">t</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4118" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>P</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>t</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>l</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>4</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>a</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-215">P_{total}=\frac{\left(1\times4\right)+\left(3\times4\right)+(6\times4)}{1+3+4}=5 atm</script></span></p>
</span>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.42em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4250" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4251" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">14.75</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4252" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1010.95em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: 0.781em; left: 0em;"><span class="mspace" id="MathJax-Span-4253" style="height: 0em; vertical-align: 0em; width: 0em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4254" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4255" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4256" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">w</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4257" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4258" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4259" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">w</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4260" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4261" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4262" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4263" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">w</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4264" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4265" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4266" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.25</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4267" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 6.682em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -6.147em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 7.053em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>,</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>R</mi><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>R</mi><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>w</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>m</mi></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>m</mi></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>w</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>w</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>15</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>298</mn></mrow><mn>303</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>14.75</mn><mi>g</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mo>∆</mo><mi>w</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>w</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>w</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0.25</mn><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-221">P_1=P_2,\ V_1=V_2 \\ \therefore n_1R T_1=n_2RT_2\Rightarrow \frac{w_1}{m}\times R\times T_1=\frac{w_2}{m}\times R\times T_2 \\ \Rightarrow w_1T_1=w_2T_2\Rightarrow w_2=\frac{w_1T_1}{T_2}=\frac{15\times 298}{303}=14.75g \\ \therefore ∆w=w_1-w_2=0.25g </script></span></p>
</span>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

            <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-228-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><msub><mi>r</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>S</mi></mrow></msub><msub><mi>r</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mrow></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi>M</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mrow></msub><msub><mi>M</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>S</mi></mrow></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>34</mn></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4302" style="width: 12.748em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.453em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.371em, 1010.45em, 3.035em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4303"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-4304"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.641em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1001.39em, 4.428em, -999.998em); top: -4.67em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.695em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4305"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.548em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>P</mi><mi>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mi>M</mi></mfrac><mi>R</mi><mi>T</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>×</mo><mi>Z</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>138.65</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>29.47</mn><mi>M</mi></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>8.314</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>293</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.85</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-237">PV=\left(\frac{m}{M}RT\right)\times Z\\ \Rightarrow138.65\times{10}^3\times10\times{10}^{-3}=\frac{29.47}{M}\times8.314\times293\times0.85 </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-238-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>M</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>44.01</mn><mo>&amp;#x2248;</mo><mn>44</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>g</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4448" style="width: 12.42em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.166em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1010.17em, 2.297em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4449"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4450" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4451" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">M<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4452" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4453" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">44.01</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4454" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≈</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4455" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">44</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4456" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4457" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4458" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4459" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4460" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4461" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">l</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4462"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.436em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.41em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4463" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">e</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-4464"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4465"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4466" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4467" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>M</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>44.01</mn><mo>≈</mo><mn>44</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>g</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-238">\Rightarrow M=44.01\approx44\ g\ mole^{-1} </script></span></p>

<p>সুতরাং, গ্যাসটির আণবিক ভর&nbsp;&nbsp;44&nbsp;g&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-239-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4468" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4469"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4470" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-239">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;গ্যাসটি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-240-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>C</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4471" style="width: 1.969em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.6em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1001.6em, 2.256em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4472"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4473" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">C<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; </span>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-4634"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4635"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4636" style="font-size: 70.7%; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4638" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">J<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4639" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">.</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4640" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.166em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4641" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4642" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">l</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4643" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">e</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4644" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4645" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">u</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4646" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">l</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4647"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.453em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-4649"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4650"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4651" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4652" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

            <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-252-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><munder><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msubsup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo></msubsup></mrow><mstyle mathsize=&quot;1.44em&quot;><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi></mrow></mstyle></munder><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mo class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot;             <div class="row">
                <div class="serial"><span>Question 57</span></div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>নির্দিষ্ট তাপমাত্রা ও চাপে একটি সরু ছিদ্র দিয়ে একটি অজ্ঞাত গ্যাসের নিঃসরণ হার ঐ একই ছিদ্র দিয়ে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-262-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>C</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4822" style="width: 2.386em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.939em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1001.94em, 2.498em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4823"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4824" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">C<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.039em;"></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4825"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.194em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.169em, 1000.75em, 4.137em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4826" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">O</span><span style="display: inline-block;             <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-263-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>x</mi></msub><msub><mi>r</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>C</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi>C</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub><msub><mi>m</mi><mi>x</mi></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>4.6</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>44</mn><msub><mi>m</mi><mi>x</mi></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi>m</mi><mi>x</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2.08</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4828" style="width: 19.1em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 15.658em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.658em, 1015.62em, 2.707em, -999.998em); vertical-align: -0.275em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.169em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-41">\rm T_1=T_2=T_3 </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">

                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>&amp;gt;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>&amp;gt;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-685" style="width: 7.47em; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-690" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.276em;">&gt;</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-691" style="padding-left: 0.276em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.141em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.19em, 1000.68em, 4.146em, -999.998em); top: -4.005em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-692" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.868em; left: 0.731em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-693" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.141em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.19em, 1000.68em, 4.146em, -999.998em); top: -4.005em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-696" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.868em; left: 0.731em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-697" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.234em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;                                             </div>

                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কোনো নির্দিষ্ট চাপ, P&nbsp;এর জন্য,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-698" style="width: 16.518em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 13.527em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1013.49em, 2.666em, -999.998em); top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-699"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-700" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-701" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-702" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-703" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-704" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-705" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-706" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-707" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">V</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-708" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-709" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">n</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-710" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-711" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-712" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-713" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">(</span></span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-714"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.617em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-715" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-716" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.62em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.617em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-717" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">)</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-718" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-719" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">V</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-720" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-721" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">T</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>∝</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-44">\rm PV=nRT\Rightarrow V=nRT\left(\frac{1}{P}\right)\therefore V\propto T</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                            <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-46-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-730" style="width: 2.143em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>আন্তঃআণবিক আকর্ষণ বলের মান <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-52-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi></mrow><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-778" style="width: 2.502em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.051em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.863em, 1002.05em, 2.625em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-779"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-780" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-781" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.322em, 1001.03em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.531em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-782"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-783"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-784" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.26em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-785" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-786" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.281em, 1000.82em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.523em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-787"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-788" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.301em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-789" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.19em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi></mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-52">\rm =\frac{n^2a}{V^2}</script></span></p>

<p>সুতরাং যার a&nbsp;এর মান বেশি, তার আন্তঃআণবিক আকর্ষণ বলও বেশি।</p>
</span>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 62</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>প্রমাণ অবস্থায় কোন গ্যাসের ব্যাপিত হতে কম সময় লাগবে?</p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-876" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-877" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.252em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mn>350</mn><mn>32</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>175</mn><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></msub></mfrac><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-62">\rm \frac{T_{O_2}}{M_{O_2}}=\frac{T_x}{M_x}\Rightarrow\frac{350}{32}=\frac{175}{M_x}\therefore M_x=16 </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-63-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-882" style="width: 0.658em; clip: rect(3.19em, 1000.46em, 4.146em, -999.998em); top: -4.005em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-902"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-903" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.6em, 1000.5em, 3.918em, -999.998em); top: -4.551em; left: 0.822em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.053em, 1000.87em, 4.328em, -999.998em); top: -4.051em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.01em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.219em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.336em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-66">\sqrt2 </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>আটগুণ বৃদ্ধিতে তাপমাত্রা হবে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-67-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-909" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-910" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-68-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; clip: rect(2.748em, 1001.03em, 4.797em, -999.998em); top: -4.055em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-941" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-947" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-948" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-949" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.174em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.797em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><mn>9</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><mi class="MJX-variant" mathvariant="normal">′</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-68">\rm \therefore\frac{C^\prime}{C}=\sqrt{\frac{T^\prime}{T}}=\sqrt{\frac{9T}{T}}=3\Rightarrow C^\prime=3C</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-69-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-950" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.6em, 1000.49em, 2.379em, -999.998em); display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-70-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-953" style="width: 4.182em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.404em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1003.36em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-954"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-955" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-956" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; margin-left: -0.449em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-957"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-958" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-959" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-960" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.99em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-961" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-962" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; </span>

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 65</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>48g মিথেন গ্যাসের জন্য কোনটি সঠিক?</p>

clip: rect(0.867em, 1000.96em, 1.186em, -999.998em); top: -1.273em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.3px solid; width: 0.959em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.05em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1059" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">)</span></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1060" style="padding-left: 0.184em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1061" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1062"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1063" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1064" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.23em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1065" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.23em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1066" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">b</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1067" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1068" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.276em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1069" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.276em;">3</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1070" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1071" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.235em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.831em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.336em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>9</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi></mrow><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">b</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-74">\rm \left(P+\frac{9a}{V^2}\right)\left(V+3b\right)=3RT </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

                                            <p>ব্রনস্টেড লাউরি মতবাদ অনুযায়ী একটি ক্ষার–<br>

                                    <p><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong></p>

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 71</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">যদি গ্যাস তিনটি বিক্রিয়া না করে তবে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-13-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-207" style="width: 2.349em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.902em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1001.9em, 2.498em, -999.998em); position: relative; width: 1.194em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.169em, 1000.71em, 4.137em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-211" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">O</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.836em; left: 0.784em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-212" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 74</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>বাস্তব গ্যাসের বৈশিষ্ট্য–<br>
(i) সব অবস্থায় বয়েলের সূত্র মেনে চলে<br>
(ii)&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-32-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Z</mi><mo>&amp;#x2260;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-457" style="width: 2.982em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.424em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1002.35em, 2.573em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-458"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-459" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Z</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-460" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">≠</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-461" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">1</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.316em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.23em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">Z</mi><mo>≠</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-32">\rm Z\neq1</script></span><br>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-35-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><msub><mi>&amp;#x2113;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>&amp;#x2113;</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mrow><mn>50</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>36.5</mn></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>20.38</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-476" style="width: 19.551em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 16.027em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.658em, 1016.03em, 2.707em, -999.998em); vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.027em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-667" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-668" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">8.314</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-669" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-670" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-671" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-672"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-673" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">35</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-674" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-675" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">273</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-676" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-677" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">J</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-678" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-679" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">480.134</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-680" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-681" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>2.5</mn><mn>20</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>8.314</mn><mo>×</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>35</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>273</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>480.134</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-49">\rm E=\frac{3}{2}nRT=\frac{3}{2}\times\frac{2.5}{20}\times8.314\times\left(35+273\right)J =480.134\ J </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-55-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>300</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><msub><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-722" style="width: 14.51em; top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-723"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-724"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.15em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-749" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-750" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>300</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><msub><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-55">\rm T_1=300K\ ;\ \ V_1=1L\ \ ;{\ V}_2=2L</script></span>&nbsp;<br>
আমরা জানি, <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-56-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>300</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mn>2</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-752" style="width: 9.551em; <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-57-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>600</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>327</mn><mo>&amp;#x2218;</mo></msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-780" style="width: 10.125em;                                     <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 82</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;"><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 160px; height: 119px;"></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">সরলরেখাটিকে নিম্নতাপমাত্রার দিকে প্রসারিত করলে x অক্ষকে যে বিন্দুতে ছেদ করবে ঐ বিন্দুর তাপমাত্রা কত?</p>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-79" style="padding-left: 0.166em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-80" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size1;">(</span></span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-81"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-82" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-83" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mn>273.15</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mn>173.15</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><msup><mn>273.15</mn><mo>∘</mo></msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-9">\rm V_t=V_0\left(1+\frac{t}{273.15}\right) \\

                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 85</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">একটি গ্যাসের 5টি অণুর গতিবেগ যথাক্রমে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-15-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-132" style="width: 4.92em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.026em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1003.99em, 2.535em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-133"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-134" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-135" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-136" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>RMS বেগ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-21-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><msup><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>4</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>5</mn></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>3.3166</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-199" style="width: 14.797em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.64em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.818em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-273"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-274" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">30</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-275" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 1.641em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: -0.08em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -4.014em; left: 0.945em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: absolute; top: -4.014em; left: 0.412em;">−<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

(ii) অভ্যন্তরীণ শক্তি আয়তনের উপর নির্ভরশীল নয়<br>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-34-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>310</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo><msub><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-382" style="width: 14.51em; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                            <p>উদ্দীপকে ভারী গ্যাসে অণুর সংখ্যা কত?</p>

<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mn>88</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-527" style="width: 2.461em; top: -2.17em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-528"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-529" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-530" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>ভারী গ্যাসের মোল সংখ্যা <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-46-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>88</mn><mn>44</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-543" style="width: 4.018em; &nbsp;হালকা গ্যাসের মোল সংখ্যা <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-47-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>20</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-551" style="width: 4.51em; ∴ হালকা গ্যাসের আংশিক চাপ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-48-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>10</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8.3</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-559" style="width: 11.805em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.674em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1009.67em, 2.502em, -999.998em); margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-563" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.723em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial"><span>Question 94</span></div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-62-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>2.5</mn><mn>20</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>8.314</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>35</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>273</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>480.134</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-817" style="width: 24.633em; width: 0px; height: 1.969em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">E</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>2.5</mn><mn>20</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>8.314</mn><mo>×</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>35</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>273</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>480.134</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-62">\rm E=\frac{3}{2}nRT=\frac{3}{2}\times\frac{2.5}{20}\times8.314\times\left(35+273\right)J =480.134\ J </script></span></p>
</span>
